  "text": "In order to verify the effectiveness of the improved multiobjective particle swarm optimization algorithm, we choose the typical multi-objective test function set ZDT [CITATION_1] and DTLZ [CITATION_2] , the representative six kinds of multi-objective functions (ZDT1, ZDT2, ZDT3, ZDT6, DTLZ1, ZTLZ4) to carry out experimental simulation comparison. In this paper, Our m=12 and \uf061\uf03d\uf031\uf030\uf030 in DTLZ4.",
